### ============================================
### 4.2 ONBOARDING ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### GET /v1/onboarding/groups
### Listar grupos disponibles (sin auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/groups

### ============================================

### POST /v1/onboarding/complete
### Finalizar onboarding y guardar grupo
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupId": "{{groupId}}",
  "username": "alex_perez",
  "birthDate": "2005-06-15"
}

### ============================================
### ERROR CASES
### ============================================

### POST /v1/onboarding/complete - Invalid date format
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupId": "{{groupId}}",
  "username": "testuser",
  "birthDate": "15/06/2005"
}

### ============================================

### POST /v1/onboarding/complete - Non-existent group
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "username": "testuser",
  "birthDate": "2005-06-15"
}

### ============================================
